Package netgame.fivecarddraw

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Main
    A main class for the network Five Card Draw Poker game.
    PokerCard
    An object of type PokerCard represents a playing card from a standard Poker deck, including Jokers.
    PokerDeck
    An object of type PokerDeck represents a deck of playing cards.
    PokerGameState
    Represents the state of a game of five-card-draw poker from one player's point of view.
    PokerHub
    A PokerHub manages a networked game of Five Card Draw Poker between two players.
    PokerRank
    This is a utility class that can be used to assign ranks to poker hands containing up to five cards.
    PokerWindow
    A window for one player in a two-player networked game of Five Card Draw Poker.
